---
---

<section class="location-section" id="location">
  <div class="container location-grid">
    <div class="location-images animate-fade-in">
      <div class="img-wrapper glass">
        <img src="/_astro/location.png" alt="Our charming piazza at sunset" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="location-content animate-fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
      <span class="eyebrow">Il Nostro Territorio</span>
      <h2>Nestled in the Heart of the Historic Center</h2>
      <p class="text-body">
        Situated in a beautiful, centuries-old cobblestone piazza, Il Sapore Autentico offers an atmosphere that is as breathtaking as its cuisine. As the sun sets, casting a golden glow over the historic architecture, our outdoor seating area becomes the perfect place to enjoy an aperitivo.
      </p>
      <p class="text-body">
        The surrounding neighborhood is rich with history, local artisans, and breathtaking views, making a visit to our restaurant a complete cultural and sensory experience.
      </p>
      
      <div class="features">
        <div class="feature-item">
          <!-- Generic icon -->
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="feature-icon"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg>
          <div>
            <h4>Historic Piazza</h4>
            <p>Picturesque views of the old city.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-item">
          <!-- Generic icon -->
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="feature-icon"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg>
          <div>
            <h4>Easy Parking</h4>
            <p>Convenient access just a short walk away.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .location-section {
    padding: 8rem 0;
    background: var(--card-bg); /* Use slightly lighter dark backround to differentiate from about section */
    border-top: 1px solid var(--card-border);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--card-border);
  }

  .location-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 5rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  /* Reverse order on mobile */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .location-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    
    .location-images {
      order: 2;
    }
    
    .location-content {
      order: 1;
    }
  }

  .eyebrow {
    color: var(--primary);
    font-family: var(--heading-font);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-style: italic;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .text-body {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .location-images {
    position: relative;
    height: 100%;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .img-wrapper {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
    position: relative;
    padding: 10px; /* To create a frame effect with glass class */
  }
  
  .img-wrapper img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
    aspect-ratio: 4/3;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 4px;
    transition: transform 0.6s ease;
  }

  .img-wrapper:hover img {
    transform: scale(1.03);
  }

  .features {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .feature-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .feature-icon {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-top: 0.2rem;
  }

  .feature-item h4 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
    color: var(--text-main);
  }

  .feature-item p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }
</style>
